{"tid":1631843,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"UC3989的士瘋狂駕駛","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T19:53:24.000Z","uid":282640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"aea57ada16a20c3d772a072fc6c64f740813ebd9","tid":1631843,"uid":282640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1477482755899091/permalink/2355809528066405?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1477482755899091%2Fpermalink%2F2355809528066405%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL9UsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=bd971812\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1477482755899091/permalink/2355809528066405?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n轉載小心駕駛group<br />\n<br />\n大約1920 本人於窩打老道向獅子山方向，由於窩打老道封路要左轉入雅息士道，期間一輛的士UC 3989 於蘭開夏道燈位撞向示威者，進入雅息士道時，本人於左線，的士駛於右線後方，的士前方有架寶馬，的士加速撞向我車右頭位置不顧而去，逆線駛入施他佛道，本人嘗試追截的士，的是駛入施他佛道時失控鏟上行人路，並撞到一位途人，本人將車攔住的士，但的士再次加速撞到我車左邊車門及車頭離去。 的士應該撞到其他車，麻煩各位在場有車cam朋友請提供更多資料。已報案"},{"pid":"347ed977b0758795f8c40878aa528d5382ece62b","tid":1631843,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:24:37.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"2684a5ed0425a4bbb45f8a3a20d166023cd17b2f","tid":1631843,"uid":282640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:33.000Z","msg":"無用10連推"},{"pid":"6844d9f6725b297f87e97aa99f5ff2bd912cbbd5","tid":1631843,"uid":282640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:26:51.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"250fe3e091e698f5bd272574bd4cdb2d1982edd2","tid":1631843,"uid":282640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:02.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"0887e746202cded4a74de2ca4f44b0926aa8e39c","tid":1631843,"uid":282640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:12.000Z","msg":"4.10"},{"pid":"1e1ca22625fd1081de88c1a137bd5c99d55cd1b7","tid":1631843,"uid":282640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:25.000Z","msg":"5.10"},{"pid":"5ed4a4a52dbcceeddb60ec0ade984a7895cf46d0","tid":1631843,"uid":282640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:41.000Z","msg":"6.10"},{"pid":"dc17e94240e935e0048f468dd87a95a9138a3f1e","tid":1631843,"uid":282640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:00.000Z","msg":"7.10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a459982d6fb4894aeefb8813716e52571f8afcf","tid":1631843,"uid":282640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:15.000Z","msg":"8.10